text": "Temporal Gyrus.", "bbox": [198.9, 757.5, 276.2, 773.0]}, {"text": "p = 1e-6). In the right MCC/precuneus, the relationships between each of the three tasks and GMV also tended", "bbox": [198.9, 805.2, 709.0, 820.9]}, {"text": "to be positively correlated with GMV (MA: r = 0.29, p = 1e-4; RAT: r = 0.15, p = 0.05; IP: r = 0.21, p = 6e-3) in", "bbox": [198.9, 818.0, 708.9, 833.7]}, {"text": "addition to a positive correlation between the ITB score and GMV (r = 0.34, p = 9e-7) (Fig. 2C). In the left CB", "bbox": [198.9, 830.8, 708.9, 846.5]}, {"text": "crus 1, scores of each of the three tasks were negatively correlated with GMV (MA: r = −0.208, p = 0.007; RAT:", "bbox": [198.9, 843.6, 708.9, 859.3]}, {"text": "r = −0.273, p = 0.0004; IP: r = −0.232, p = 0.003). In the right SMA, scores of each of the three tasks were also", "bbox": [199.0, 856.4, 709.0, 872.0]}, {"text": "negatively correlated with GMV (MA: r = −0.222, p = 0.004; RAT: r = −0.135, p = 0.09; IP: r = −0.255, p = 0.001)", "bbox": [199.0, 869.1, 708.9, 884.8]}, {"text": "(Fig. 2D). These results suggest that the brain regions identified by the VBM analysis were significantly correlated", "bbox": [198.9, 882.1, 709.1, 897.6]}, {"text": "with not only the ITB score but also each task score, although significance levels between the task score and GMV", "bbox": [198.9, 894.9, 708.8, 910.4]}, {"text": "were different.", "bbox": [198.9, 907.6, 264.5, 923.2]}, {"text": "SCIeNTIfIC RepORTS | (2018) 8:6477 | DOI:10.1038/s41598-018-24981-0 4", "bbox": [52.1, 964.7, 708.9, 979.9]}]}